snippet.textDisplay:
I think it's a grave insult to their talents if any of these two singers are compared to each other. Both their parts were almost equally hard and delicate from their respective sides including the parts of the instrumentalists and other musicians as far as I've realized. They just had one of the best performances of their lives. And what a lyric it was! Undoubtedly song of the season for me. It will be tough even to guess how many times I've played it already. 
Respect to Pakistani Singers from the core of my heart.
From Bangladesh.
